longBusinessSummary: Medfield Diagnostics AB (publ) develops and sells medical devices based on microwave technology. The company offers Strokefinder MD100, a device for decision-support to assist in clinical evaluation and triage of suspected intracranial injuries in the acute situation. Medfield Diagnostics AB (publ) was incorporated in 2005 and is based in Gothenburg, Sweden.
